===============================================================================

SurveyEngine Installation Complete!

===============================================================================

What was installed:

  Configuration:
    config/initializers/survey_engine.rb
    config/initializers/locale.rb

  Translations:
    config/locales/survey_engine.es.yml
    config/locales/survey_engine.en.yml

Next Steps:

  1. Configure your authentication method in config/initializers/survey_engine.rb
     - For Devise: config.current_user_email_method = lambda { current_user&.email }
     - For other systems: modify as needed

  2. Add routes to config/routes.rb:
     mount SurveyEngine::Engine => "/surveys"

  3. Optional: Generate custom controller for advanced customization:
     rails generate survey_engine:install --controller

  4. Run migrations:
     rails survey_engine:install:migrations
     rails db:migrate

  5. Create your first survey using Rails console or seeds:
     SurveyEngine::Survey.create!(title: "My Survey", description: "...")

Documentation: https://github.com/your-repo/survey_engine

